OL,4,CBooks: Bid for more diverse heroes in
OL,5,CWelsh children's stories
OL,6, More diverse heroes and heroines are
OL,7, needed in Welsh children's stories to
OL,8, inspire black and ethnic minority
OL,9, children, authors have said.
OL,11,FWriter Jessica Dunrod said many
OL,12,Fchildren wanted to change their hair
OL,13,Fand skin to look like their favourite
OL,14,Fcharacters, who were mostly white.
OL,16,FThe Cardiff author said it was "vital"
OL,17,Fblack children saw themselves in books.
OL,19,FLiterature Wales said the lack of
OL,20,Fdiversity in books made people feel
OL,21,F"like they don't belong".
